{"tid":854363,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知過唔過到試用期好糾結","createTime":"2018-10-09T09:59:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T08:19:38.000Z","uid":187771,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"afeaaa84c5cb051ce8af4cadf267a8c0c6126a44","tid":854363,"uid":187771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:59:02.000Z","msg":"聽同事講做左一個月左右，上司會搵我問下做成點<br />\n但係冇<br />\n宜家就黎兩個月都冇<br />\n<br />\n聽聞兩個月左右都會搵我傾下<br />\n到宜家都未😩😫<br />\n<br />\n上司仲要勁cool，見親佢都係黑面<br />\n勁驚🤦🏻&zwj;♀️<br />\n<br />\n日日都糾結緊係咪唔打算請我，所以都費時搵我🤦🏻&zwj;♀️"},{"pid":"a73a7479bd04cef35530ca3fdea4d5c9a8d8b60b","tid":854363,"uid":33539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T10:10:30.000Z","msg":"聽日遞信好過到時佢炒你呀"},{"pid":"6f454a25c788a48c11b5f2a75335ff0398a0d38e","tid":854363,"uid":187771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a73a7479bd04cef35530ca3fdea4d5c9a8d8b60b","tid":854363,"uid":33539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T10:10:30.000Z","msg":"聽日遞信好過到時佢炒你呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T10:14:41.000Z","msg":"我想係度做落去呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以每日都好擔心<br />\n<br />\n其實我有諗過會唔會因為我完全係外行人<br />\n所以之前都冇搵我傾諗住等我做熟先<br />\n<br />\n雖然我覺得係過份樂觀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e1eb58a64dad38a4b9b69a40f362acdefbe2648","tid":854363,"uid":154505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T11:39:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇人記得你仲係試用期<br />\n比心機做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">冇人記得你存在根本<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"8cf33d8457dd1ae84328be79a37ff3c03f31006b","tid":854363,"uid":59283,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T12:02:41.000Z","msg":"唔係好on9都會比你過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgm